</a>
                                                                                                        <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20220721143513/https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https%3A%2F%2Ff24.my%2F5PIw.T&amp;via=Observers&amp;related=Observers&amp;text=African%20migrants%20trapped%20in%20Mexico%20protest%20for%20right%20to%20travel%20to%20USA&amp;lang=en" class="m-share-bar__link a-picto-social svg" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" aria-label="Twitter"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="489 48 45 45"><path d="M529.516 48h-36.032A4.473 4.473 0 0 0 489 52.484v36.032A4.473 4.473 0 0 0 493.484 93h36.032A4.473 4.473 0 0 0 534 88.516V52.484A4.473 4.473 0 0 0 529.516 48zm-5.4 15.288v.918c0 8.535-6.537 18.475-18.475 18.475a18.91 18.91 0 0 1-9.886-2.917h1.564a14.7 14.7 0 0 0 8.1-2.7 6.475 6.475 0 0 1-6.05-4.484 10.794 10.794 0 0 1 1.134.216 5.05 5.05 0 0 0 1.783-.216 6.488 6.488 0 0 1-5.186-6.321 14.226 14.226 0 0 0 2.917.918c-1.779-1.62-2.917-3.403-2.917-5.672a4.878 4.878 0 0 1 .918-3.133 18.2 18.2 0 0 0 13.289 6.753c0-.432-.216-.918-.216-1.567a6.525 6.525 0 0 1 6.537-6.537 6.4 6.4 0 0 1 4.754 2 11.338 11.338 0 0 0 4.052-1.567 6.631 6.631 0 0 1-2.917 3.619 11.518 11.518 0 0 0 3.836-1.134 15.992 15.992 0 0 1-3.241 3.349z" fill="#28a9e0"/></svg>
</a>
                                                                                                                                                            
